# Core Project Conventions

## Monorepo placement

| Change type | Location |
|-------------|----------|
| Mobile H5 UI / routes | `apps/h5` |
| Pad + PC UI / routes | `apps/web` |
| Shared UI components | `packages/ui` (`shadcn add` targets ui package) |
| HTTP client & endpoints | `packages/api` |
| Request/response DTOs | `packages/shared-types` |
| App env & API bootstrap | `apps/*/src/lib/env.ts`, `apps/*/src/lib/api.ts` |

Never duplicate API calls or DTOs across apps. UI differs; data layer is shared.

## Language

- Code, comments, and developer-facing errors: **English**
- Git commits: **English**, conventional commits (`feat(scope): subject`)
- End-user UI copy may be Chinese when product requires it

## Commands

```bash
pnpm dev:h5    # :5173
pnpm dev:web   # :5174
pnpm build && pnpm test && pnpm typecheck && pnpm audit
```

## Security

Run `pnpm audit` before merging. Resolve critical/high vulnerabilities.
